name: ABC
text:
Protesters gathered outside the County Justice Center in Minnesota, as the pretrial hearing of the four former officers charged in the killing of George Floyd took place.

The four ex-officers were later seen going back to jail following the hearing. https://t.co/P8FagilDpQ https://t.co/Skhdciu9h4

name: ABC
text:
A rare albino seal pup was spotted in Russia with a uniquely ginger coat, although researchers worry it could face rejection from the colony.

The photographer noted the pup looked well fed and was not being bothered by the other seals, a good sign. https://t.co/j78VLvp1JO https://t.co/h7Pd0lKy0u
